    "title": "Principal Investment Banker at Grant Thornton India South Asia Partners",
    "description": "Grow your career with Grant Thornton India South Asia Partners! We are hiring a Investment Banker for our Raipur team. Be part of a workplace that celebrates innovation, diversity, and performance.\n\nAbout Grant Thornton India South Asia Partners:\nGrant Thornton India South Asia Partners is a leading organization in the Remote sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Manage accounts payable and accounts receivable functions\n• Conduct due diligence for mergers, acquisitions, and investments\n• Coordinate with external auditors during annual audits\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in Python for Finance\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in Tally\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in SQL\n\nWork Mode: Remote - Work from anywhere in India\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Learning & development budget\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Employee stock options (ESOPs) for eligible roles\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Raipur, Chhattisgarh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Grant Thornton India South Asia Partners!",
